{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/2021-02-13-migrate-to-gatsby/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"60d0be7f-f8b3-5c7d-98c9-ce142d7268e8","html":"<h2 id=\"為何要改用-gatsbyjs-架構\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E8%A6%81%E6%94%B9%E7%94%A8-gatsbyjs-%E6%9E%B6%E6%A7%8B\" aria-label=\"為何要改用 gatsbyjs 架構 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>為何要改用 Gatsby.js 架構</h2>\n<p>我從2015年左右開始寫部落格，一開始是開在 <a href=\"https://logdown.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Logdown</a> 平台上，後來因為它停止維護了，於是改用 <a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-tw/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Hexo</a> 自己建，並託管在 Github Pages 上。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/d9ed5/old-blog.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/8ac56/old-blog.webp 240w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/d3be9/old-blog.webp 480w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/e46b2/old-blog.webp 960w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/f992d/old-blog.webp 1440w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/882b9/old-blog.webp 1920w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/d3d72/old-blog.webp 2880w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/8ff5a/old-blog.png 240w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/e85cb/old-blog.png 480w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/d9199/old-blog.png 960w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/07a9c/old-blog.png 1440w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/29114/old-blog.png 1920w,\n/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/d9ed5/old-blog.png 2880w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/fddb66e0269836b34fc4ced4fcb801ad/d9199/old-blog.png\"\n            alt=\"舊部落格\"\n            title=\"舊部落格\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>而現在會想改架構原因如下：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>前陣子因為在忙畢業和當兵，好一陣子沒更新部落格了，而且又換了新筆電，舊的 Hexo 設定要花時間重新熟悉</li>\n<li>這兩年都在玩 React.js，一直很想用 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gatsby.js</a> 這套基於 React.js 的靜態網頁生成框架來做點什麼</li>\n<li>當完兵過年期間閒得蛋疼，想學點新技術恢復開發手感</li>\n</ol>\n<p>於是決定用 Gatsby.js 來重架部落格啦！</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/d9ed5/gatsby.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/8ac56/gatsby.webp 240w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/d3be9/gatsby.webp 480w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/e46b2/gatsby.webp 960w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/f992d/gatsby.webp 1440w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/882b9/gatsby.webp 1920w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/d3d72/gatsby.webp 2880w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/8ff5a/gatsby.png 240w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/e85cb/gatsby.png 480w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/d9199/gatsby.png 960w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/07a9c/gatsby.png 1440w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/29114/gatsby.png 1920w,\n/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/d9ed5/gatsby.png 2880w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a92a9cecf0de45d36003dafb7772ad41/d9199/gatsby.png\"\n            alt=\"Gatsby.js官網\"\n            title=\"Gatsby.js官網\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"搬遷過程\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%90%AC%E9%81%B7%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B\" aria-label=\"搬遷過程 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>搬遷過程</h2>\n<p>之前用 Hexo 時，30篇文章是 Markdown 格式的 .md 檔，檔案都還留著，而 Gatsby.js 也支援使用 .md 檔來生成靜態頁面，和 Hexo 的運作邏輯基本一致。</p>\n<p>因此搬遷流程不會太複雜：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>用 Gatsby 建立新專案</li>\n<li>把 30 個文章 .md 檔移過去</li>\n<li>調整新部落格設定（樣式、頁面配置、Domain設定等）</li>\n<li>生成靜態頁面再丟上 Github Pages，就算是搬遷完成了</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"1-用-gatsby-建立新專案\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%E7%94%A8-gatsby-%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E5%B0%88%E6%A1%88\" aria-label=\"1 用 gatsby 建立新專案 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 用 Gatsby 建立新專案</h3>\n<p>這部分我卡最久，主要是 Gatsby 生態圈太大，有太多方式可以建立起一個 Gatsby 網站，很多選擇需要決定。</p>\n<p>我不想花太多時間在搬遷，而是想專注在寫文章，但因為我後續想要深度客製化我的部落格，所以花了不少時間在思考各個方案：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>自己架、或是託管在 Gatsby Cloud 上？ <strong>自己架，比較容易客製化，也不用花錢</strong></li>\n<li>需不需要 CMS？要的話要哪套？ <strong>先不用，CMS 我不熟，研究起來沒完沒了，先成功搬遷我 30 篇文章即可</strong></li>\n<li>靜態檔要 Host 在哪裡？ <strong>Github Pages，之前就是在這裡，用起來很舒服、穩定，沒有理由換</strong></li>\n<li>要從頭開始建 Gatsby 專案，還是從 starter 專案開始？ <strong>找 starter 專案開始，想趕快搬遷完成，從頭建太慢</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>於是我瀏覽了 Gatsby 的 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/starters/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">starter 列表</a> ，找了下面這套順眼的樣板開始建專案：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/starters/alxshelepenok/gatsby-starter-lumen/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">gatsby-starter-lumen\n</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/97755/lumen-starter.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/8ac56/lumen-starter.webp 240w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/d3be9/lumen-starter.webp 480w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/e46b2/lumen-starter.webp 960w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/f992d/lumen-starter.webp 1440w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/882b9/lumen-starter.webp 1920w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/16df7/lumen-starter.webp 2536w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/8ff5a/lumen-starter.png 240w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/e85cb/lumen-starter.png 480w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/d9199/lumen-starter.png 960w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/07a9c/lumen-starter.png 1440w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/29114/lumen-starter.png 1920w,\n/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/97755/lumen-starter.png 2536w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6ae24a416f21dfbee4d26b330b964a29/d9199/lumen-starter.png\"\n            alt=\"lumen starter\"\n            title=\"lumen starter\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>按照裡面的教學建立起了專案：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> global <span class=\"token function\">add</span> gatsby-cli <span class=\"token comment\"># 若沒 gatsby-cli 的話，才須先安裝</span>\n\ngatsby new my-blog https://github.com/alxshelepenok/gatsby-starter-lumen\n\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> my-blog\ngatsby develop <span class=\"token comment\"># 啟動 local server</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>跑完後就可以用瀏覽器開 <code class=\"language-text\">http://localhost:8000</code> 在自己電腦上看到新部落格了</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-把-30-個文章-md-檔移過去\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%E6%8A%8A-30-%E5%80%8B%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0-md-%E6%AA%94%E7%A7%BB%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB\" aria-label=\"2 把 30 個文章 md 檔移過去 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 把 30 個文章 .md 檔移過去</h3>\n<p>把 .md 檔放到新專案的 <strong>/content/posts/</strong> 底下 </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 866px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c964849f3289b3892b752235d9bf6f65/c1328/move-posts.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 107.91666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c964849f3289b3892b752235d9bf6f65/8ac56/move-posts.webp 240w,\n/static/c964849f3289b3892b752235d9bf6f65/d3be9/move-posts.webp 480w,\n/static/c964849f3289b3892b752235d9bf6f65/e299d/move-posts.webp 866w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 866px) 100vw, 866px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c964849f3289b3892b752235d9bf6f65/8ff5a/move-posts.png 240w,\n/static/c964849f3289b3892b752235d9bf6f65/e85cb/move-posts.png 480w,\n/static/c964849f3289b3892b752235d9bf6f65/c1328/move-posts.png 866w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 866px) 100vw, 866px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c964849f3289b3892b752235d9bf6f65/c1328/move-posts.png\"\n            alt=\"搬遷所有文章\"\n            title=\"搬遷所有文章\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>然後調整各文章的 metadata，符合新專案的命名和格式，重點是 draft 要設成 false，才能看到文章！</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/ea64c/update-post-metadata.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.91666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/8ac56/update-post-metadata.webp 240w,\n/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/d3be9/update-post-metadata.webp 480w,\n/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/e46b2/update-post-metadata.webp 960w,\n/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/36c36/update-post-metadata.webp 1116w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/8ff5a/update-post-metadata.png 240w,\n/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/e85cb/update-post-metadata.png 480w,\n/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/d9199/update-post-metadata.png 960w,\n/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/ea64c/update-post-metadata.png 1116w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/88efe16ad2df85a3eb2aeff3e11e6726/d9199/update-post-metadata.png\"\n            alt=\"更新 metadata\"\n            title=\"更新 metadata\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"3-調整新部落格設定（樣式、頁面配置、domain設定等）\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%83%A8%E8%90%BD%E6%A0%BC%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%EF%BC%88%E6%A8%A3%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%81%E9%A0%81%E9%9D%A2%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E3%80%81domain%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E7%AD%89%EF%BC%89\" aria-label=\"3 調整新部落格設定（樣式、頁面配置、domain設定等） permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 調整新部落格設定（樣式、頁面配置、Domain設定等）</h3>\n<p>再來就是調整細部內容成我想要的樣子，部落格 title、社群連結、網址、Disqus連結、favicon 等，主要是調整 <strong>config.js</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token string\">'use strict'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  url<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://www.easonchang.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  pathPrefix<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  title<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Eason\\'s Playground - blog by Eason Chang'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  subtitle<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Let\\'s make something awesome!\\n'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  copyright<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'© All rights reserved.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  disqusShortname<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'xxxxxxxxxxxxx'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  postsPerPage<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  googleAnalyticsId<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'G-XXXXXXXXX'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  useKatex<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  menu<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      label<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'文章'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      path<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/'</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      label<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'關於我'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      path<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/pages/about'</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      label<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'專案'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      path<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/pages/projects'</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  author<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Eason Chang'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    photo<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/bio-img.jpeg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    bio<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Hi, I am Eason!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    contacts<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      email<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'eason@easonchang.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      facebook<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'chang.ying.hsiang'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      telegram<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      twitter<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      github<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Kamigami55'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      rss<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      vkontakte<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      linkedin<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'easonchang101'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      instagram<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      line<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      gitlab<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      weibo<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      codepen<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      youtube<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      soundcloud<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      medium<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"4-生成靜態頁面再丟上-github-pages，就算是搬遷完成了\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E9%9D%9C%E6%85%8B%E9%A0%81%E9%9D%A2%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%9F%E4%B8%8A-github-pages%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E7%AE%97%E6%98%AF%E6%90%AC%E9%81%B7%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%BA%86\" aria-label=\"4 生成靜態頁面再丟上 github pages，就算是搬遷完成了 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 生成靜態頁面再丟上 Github Pages，就算是搬遷完成了</h3>\n<p>我原本的 Hexo 部落格就是架在 Github Pages 上，repo 是 <a href=\"https://github.com/Kamigami55/Kamigami55.github.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Kamigami55/Kamigami55.github.io</a> ，網址會是 <a href=\"https://Kamigami55.github.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Kamigami55.github.io</a> 。</p>\n<p>另外原本就還有在 GoDaddy 上買網域指向這個位置，所以部落格最終網址會是\n<a href=\"https://www.easonchang.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.easonchang.com/</a> 。</p>\n<p>而我現在做的動作是把舊 repo 改名封存，重開一個新的 <strong>Kamigami55/Kamigami55.github.io</strong> repo，並把剛剛編輯好的 gatsby 專案 push 到 master branch 存放原始碼。</p>\n<p>然後在終端機執行以下指令，建立新部落格的靜態檔，並會自動 push 到 gh-pages branch。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> deploy</code></pre></div>\n<p>最後在 Github repo 設定頁開啟 Github Pages 功能，按照下圖的方式設定：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/8963a/pages-setting.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/8ac56/pages-setting.webp 240w,\n/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/d3be9/pages-setting.webp 480w,\n/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/e46b2/pages-setting.webp 960w,\n/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/f992d/pages-setting.webp 1440w,\n/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/c5cbd/pages-setting.webp 1918w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/8ff5a/pages-setting.png 240w,\n/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/e85cb/pages-setting.png 480w,\n/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/d9199/pages-setting.png 960w,\n/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/07a9c/pages-setting.png 1440w,\n/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/8963a/pages-setting.png 1918w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/ffbaaa7799bc6cc99ebca44e9d987895/d9199/pages-setting.png\"\n            alt=\"Pages設定\"\n            title=\"Pages設定\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>就可以看到全新的部落格上線了！</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.easonchang.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.easonchang.com/</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/8bd7d/new-blog.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.83333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/8ac56/new-blog.webp 240w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/d3be9/new-blog.webp 480w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/e46b2/new-blog.webp 960w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/f992d/new-blog.webp 1440w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/882b9/new-blog.webp 1920w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/aacf5/new-blog.webp 2358w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/8ff5a/new-blog.png 240w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/e85cb/new-blog.png 480w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/d9199/new-blog.png 960w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/07a9c/new-blog.png 1440w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/29114/new-blog.png 1920w,\n/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/8bd7d/new-blog.png 2358w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6a51e343ab3768633954c68472e60b4a/d9199/new-blog.png\"\n            alt=\"全新 Eason&#39;s Playground 部落格\"\n            title=\"全新 Eason&#39;s Playground 部落格\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"troubleshooting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#troubleshooting\" aria-label=\"troubleshooting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Troubleshooting</h2>\n<h3 id=\"調整每頁的顯示的文章數量\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E6%AF%8F%E9%A0%81%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%95%B8%E9%87%8F\" aria-label=\"調整每頁的顯示的文章數量 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>調整每頁的顯示的文章數量</h3>\n<p>我找的模板預設每頁只顯示 4 篇文章，實在太少了，我想改成每頁顯示 10 篇文章。<strong>config.js</strong> 內有 <strong>postsPerPage</strong> 參數可以直接調整，但調了以後無效。</p>\n<p>研究了大半天後發現應該是 gatsby 傳遞 context 時 type 沒有設定到，需要修改 <strong>/src/types/index.js</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> type PageContext <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  tag<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  category<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  currentPage<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> number<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  prevPagePath<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  nextPagePath<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  hasPrevPage<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> boolean<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  hasNextPage<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> boolean<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  postsLimit<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> number <span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;--- add this</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>我有在 <a href=\"https://github.com/alxshelepenok/gatsby-starter-lumen/issues/660#issuecomment-778575664\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">這個 issue</a> 回覆一些想法，研究更清楚後若確定是個 bug，會發 PR 把它修掉。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"心得＆未來方向\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97%EF%BC%86%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91\" aria-label=\"心得＆未來方向 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>心得＆未來方向</h2>\n<p>整個搬遷花了我一整天的時間，以前的設定太久沒碰，又沒有寫文章記錄，真的會忘光光，很浪費之前投入的時間，於是這次決定一定要寫文章紀錄自己搬遷的流程，給未來的自己備忘。</p>\n<p>未來應該還會寫很多部落格調校文章，還有很多東西想修改，像是深度客製化樣式、加入 GA 追蹤、深色主題、文章編輯流程優化等，期待後續的發展！</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2021-02-13-migrate-to-gatsby/","tagSlugs":["/tag/blog/","/tag/gatsby/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-02-13T05:57:00.983Z","description":"當完兵過年期間閒的蛋疼，想要嘗試新技術，於是決定用 Gatsby.js 來重架部落格啦！","tags":["Blog","Gatsby"],"title":"部落格搬遷紀錄，用 Gatsby.js 取代 Hexo","socialImage":"./new-blog.png"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2021-02-13-migrate-to-gatsby/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}